snippet.title: Outlive - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
You can wishlist Outlive on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2338120/Outlive/

Outlive is an intense game of survival! Run, hide and outsmart mutants in a post-apocalyptic world. No fighting allowed, only puzzles to solve. Created by an indie studio founded by a father and son.

Coming out 14 Sep, 2023

https://bosscogames.com/
